title: GIANT Emotions
itunes:title: GIANT Emotions
description:
TUE 10/4 - On the heels of the NY Giants' loss to the Minnesota Vikings, The Breakfast Club discusses whether or not Odell Beckham's emotions are messing up his money. A big hee-haw for the Blonde Burst of Big Blue. We also tackle the issue of "social media flossing". Hide your wife, hide your kids...and hide those pics of you stuntin' on 'em!
